reviewText: Great product and delivered in time. I would order again.
We're very happy with this purchase. Haven't owned it for very long, but no problems at all so far!

This was a cool video to see.  A candid chat with Mike P and a cool little jam session with Mike and Bozio.  It was cool to watch, but for the price (I paid around $25), I can't suggest it.  Just something nice to have in the collection of Portnoy stuff :)
